" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.308</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; of a cloud of dust, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὕψι δ᾽ ἀέλλη σκίδναθ᾽ ὑπὸ νεφέων</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:16:375\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">16.375</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; of a stream, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀνὰ κῆπον ἅπαντα σκίδναται</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:7:130\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.130</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; also <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὀδμὴ σκίδνατο</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0013.tlg002.perseus-grc1:278\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">h.Cer.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">278</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὂψ σκιδναμένη</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0020.tlg001.perseus-grc1:42\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hes.\">Hes.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">42</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">σκιδναμένα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0261.tlg001:41\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Simon.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">41</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> codd.<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> </bibl> (<xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">f.l. for</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">κιδν-</ref> </xr>); <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σκιδ