.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">48</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> <abbr TEIform=\"abbr\">=</abbr> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0627.tlg053:3\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Dieb.Judic.\">Dieb.Judic.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3</biblScope> </bibl>; elsewh. rare in Prose, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0093.tlg003:55\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Thphr.\">Thphr.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Sens.\">Sens.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">55</biblScope></bibl>,<bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0093.tlg003:56\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">56</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">εὐωδία ἐκ πηγῆς -αμένη</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.941f</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (not found in good <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Att.\">Att.</a></gram></gramGrp>, except compd. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀποσκίδναμαι</foreign> in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0003.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:98\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Th.\">Th.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.98</biblScope> </bibl>).</sense> </entryFree>"}]}